            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:f10a76d1-456b-4412-9097-a35b009a43d3</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/lean_manufacturing/~3/ZM_QJUzzqMo/lean-best-practice</link>
