            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:224d9a3f-e847-4478-b2da-a0d100de2007</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/lean_manufacturing/~3/2VEx_5YhIFo/communicate-build-culture</link>
