            <title>Six Sigma's focus on critical to quality measures</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	Six Sigma focuses on critical to quality (CTQ) measures of delay, defects and deviation. These are used with control charts and histograms to focus, improve and sustain improvements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/lean_manufacturing/~4/IKYolgi_5gk" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
