            <title>Address waste, rework, defects with 4-50 Rule</title>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	Learn the 4-50 Rule:&amp;nbsp;Four percent&amp;nbsp;of the steps in any process cause 50% of the waste, rework, defects, deviation and lost profit. Use Pareto charts to narrow your focus to the 4% to maximize results and profit.&lt;br /&gt;
	&lt;br /&gt;
	&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/lean_manufacturing/~4/aZBHOBLf_e0" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
