            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:f7baad0b-50e3-4d39-843c-9e21008e4c0d</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/lean_manufacturing/~3/XbXASPCkJUQ/Tougher-competition-smarter-production</link>
