            <title>Intel applies lean methods outside of the plant</title>
            <description>&lt;p id="eow-description"&gt;
	Intel&amp;#39;s Site Materials group in New Mexico applied lean manufacturing principles to Albuquerque&amp;#39;s Road-Runner Food Bank, dramatically improving the time it takes to pack food boxes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/lean_manufacturing/~4/Z0GVzU58s-c" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
